name: Freeje
overview:
Freeje - is an application for mobile phones and smartphones that allows to make cheap international calls. The application is supported by such popular platforms as IPhone, Android, Windows Mobile, Blackberry and Java Me. There are no special skills required for the installation .All you have to do is to create your account, download the application on the mobile phone and to top up your balance, afterward you can freely make your calls. The application can be used in every country with available GSM network. Put in a SIM card of local operator and change number in the application settings to make cheap phone calls. Then just run the application and make cheap phone calls.

Skype calls: Freeje allows to make a free callback to Skype even if Wi-Fi is not available in the area

Calls to other phones: At the moment Freeje works so that both of subscribers receive incoming calls. Dialer enters subscriber’s phone number then he receives an incoming call, subscriber receives an incoming call as well.
